    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK892">
<l>periyāraip pēṇā toḻukiṟ periyārāṟ</l>
<l>pērā viṭumpai tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To behave without respect for the great (rulers) will make them do (us) irremediable evils.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
